    "created_at": "2015-08-28T17:53:40Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-08-28T17:56:21Z",
    "body": "also getting this bug on mac, I have a hack workaround while this is getting fixed:\n- set `resizable: true` in BrowserWindow opts (makes window correct height)\n- to stop resizing. in main.js/index.js:\n\n``` javascript\nmainWindow.on('resize', function(e) {\ne.preventDefault();\nmainWindow.setContentSize(origW, origH);\n});\n```\n\nit's a dirty hack I'd prefer not to do, hopefully this bug is fixed soon.\n"
